                        How can a Pacific Gas & Electric bill be paid online?






As of 2015, a Pacific Gas & Electric (PG&E) bill can be paid online through the energy company's My Energy program or through EZ-Pay, which is a third-party payment service. The PG&E My Energy online payment system requi...

