                        Which methods of payment are accepted by Pacific Gas and Electric Company?

As of 2015, The Pacific Gas and Electric Company accepts Visa, MasterCard, debit or bank account transfers for payments made over the phone at 877-704-8470. Checks are accepted via mail, and bank, Visa, MasterCard and de...

