Which methods of payment are accepted by Pacific Gas and Electric Company?

As of 2015, The Pacific Gas and Electric Company accepts Visa, MasterCard, debit or bank account transfers for payments made over the phone at 877-704-8470. Checks are accepted via mail, and bank, Visa, MasterCard and de...

                            More »


www.reference.com
› Business & Finance
› Personal Banking





How do you pay a Mohave Electric bill online?

Pay a Mohave Electric bill by utilizing the SmartHub online bill payment service, using the Easy Pay Service, or using the computers at the Member Services office in Bullhead City. Payments are also accepted by phone.

                            More »


www.reference.com
› Business & Finance
› Personal Banking





What payment options are available to pay your PGE bill online?

Pacific Gas and Electric online bill payment options include a My Energy account through the PGE website or using the EZ Pay bill-payment system. As of 2015, paying a PGE bill through a My Energy account is free and ther...

