									Event Day(s)
								





1SmartRate™ Alert
ALERT TYPE: Information


July 27 is a SmartDay. Manage your energy use between 2-7 p.m. SmartAC users will be activated.
Learn how to Reduce your electricity use on SmartDays






2Peak Day Pricing Event Day
ALERT TYPE: Information


July 27 is a Peak Day Pricing Event Day. Event Day hours are from 2-6 p.m.
Learn how to start saving on event days






3SmartAC™ Alert
ALERT TYPE: Information


July 27 is a SmartAC Event Day. Between 2:30 p.m. - 7:00 p.m. some ACs will cycle for no more than 4.0 hours.
Learn more about SmartAC event days













