Tune in to see the falcon chicks

Exciting news! Several chicks have hatched on the ledge of the 33rd floor of our San Francisco headquarters. Watch our live webcam to see the falcon parents feed and care for their fluffy nestlings.


Visit the peregrine falcons













Avoid spikes in energy bills

PG&E's free Budget Billing averages your energy costs to help make monthly payments more predictable.


Enroll in Budget Billing













Free energy saving tools at your fingertips

Online tools in Your Account can give you insight into your summer energy use, helping you stay cool while you save.


