Pacific Gas & Electric Company Careers




































































































Open MenuHide Menu

















HomeYou are here: Home
 

Together, Building a Better California.
There aren’t many opportunities to do something really big. To impact the lives of millions of your friends, family and neighbors. This is what we offer you at PG&E. We deliver innovative energy solutions to 15 million Californians, from the Central Valley to Silicon Valley, all the way to the Oregon border. Join us as we build a better California.
Opportunities in progress.

 

Search JobsKeywordsJob CategoriesSelect Job CategoryAccounting / FinanceAdministrative / ClericalBusiness Operations / StrategyCompliance / Risk / Quality AssuranceCustomer Support / OperationsEnergy Supply / TradingEngineering / ScienceInformation TechnologyLegalMaintenance / Construction / OperationsNuclear GenerationProcurement / Supply ChainCity, State or Zip Returning visitors, log into your Talent Profile to update your profile or check your application status.


Before You Login
Thank you for your interest in PG&E. Before you login, please note:

The job search function is offline for maintenance every Saturday night, from 9:00pm to 9:30pm (Pacific).
This site works best if you have one of the following browsers installed: Internet Explorer 9-11; Firefox 45; Safari 9.0 (on Mac OS 10.11); or Chrome 54.
This site does not support mobile browsers.

Continue to Login





 
