Contact us













You can reach PG&E anytime, day or night, seven days a week by phone or online.












If you smell natural gas, see downed power lines, or suspect another emergency situation, leave the area immediately and call 9-1-1. Then, call PG&E at 1-800-743-5000.

Have a question about your bill or usage amount? Before you call, save time and read the answers to our top questions.












Self-serve options

Take care of tasks quickly and easily online. Pay your bill, start or stop service, get financial assistance and more. The options below will take you straight to your request. You can also visit our online Help Center.










Residential: Account, billing and payment









Select the topic below that best fits your needs. For most options, you'll need to provide your PG&E account number or sign in to your online account. Don't have an online account? Sign up today.


Check balance online
View or pay current bill
High bill? Learn ways to save
How to find your current bill online
Make a payment:

Online recurring payments
One-time credit card payment
Pay-in-person locations
Installments/arrangements


Enroll in paperless billing
Keep payments predictable with Budget Billing
Learn about payment assistance programs
Update your bank account information
Update your address or phone number
How to waive your security deposit
What to do about service shutoff for non-payment












Residential: Financial assistance









Select the topic that best fits your needs


Request a payment arrangement to allow more time to pay
Learn more about payment arrangements
Keep payments predictable with Budget Billing
Discount programs:

CARE: California Alternate Rates for Energy
FERA: Family Electric Rate Assistance
REACH: one-time assistance
Medical Baseline Allowance


Find out how to have your deposit waived












Business: Account, billing and payment









Select the topic below that best fits your needs. For most options, you'll need to provide your PG&E account number or sign in to your online account. Don't have an online account? Sign Up today.


