Set other notifications


For more information about Notifications and Alerts, visit Frequently Asked Questions.

















Contact us










Call Us









24-hour Power Outage Information Center 1-800-743-5002

24-hour Residential Customer Service Center English: 1-877-660-6789 Español: 1-877-660-6789 中文: 1-800-893-9555 Tiếng Việt: 1-800-298-8438 TTD/TTY: Hours of Operation:1-800-652-4712

Monday – Friday: 9 a.m. - 11 p.m.
Call 711 (California Relay Service) anytime


Business Customer Service Center Monday-Friday, 7 a.m. - 6 p.m. 1-800-468-4743

Agricultural Customer Service Center Monday-Friday, 7 a.m.- 6 p.m. 1-877-311-3276

Call Before You Dig 811

Call us and use our interactive voice response system to:

Access account information
Make a payment
Contact billing transactions
Connect, disconnect, or change service
Report on outage












Email Us









Send a messageVISIT the Online Contact Form











Visit Us









PG&E Customer Service Centers and neighborhood payment center locations:Visit Our Payment Center Locator

Services Available:

Bill payment (cash, check, money order or cashier's check)
Customer service
Self-Service Quick Pay Bill Payment kiosks that accept cash, check, or Visa/MasterCard payments are available at select offices. If applicable: does not provide change and $1.25 fee for Visa/MasterCard. Payments made before 5 p.m. are posted same day. Visit Payment Center Locator for more information












Write Us









Send correspondence to:Pacific Gas and Electric Company P.O. Box 997300 Sacramento, CA 95899-7300











Other Important Numbers









Building and Renovation Service Center 1-877-743-7782

Charitable Contributions 415-973-4951

Diablo Canyon Power Plant 1-805-546-5292

Shareholder Information 1-888-489-4689

Smarter Energy Line 1-800-933-9555

Solar Customer Service Center1-877-743-4112

Supplier Diversity 415-973-8800











Special Services









Vision Impaired Request large print service, a braille bill or schedule an appointment for household appliance braille marking services. Visit Language Services 1-800-743-5000

Deaf/Hard of Hearing/Speech We provide help for our deaf, hard of hearing, and visually-impaired customers, and customers who have a speech disability with various services.For TTY, you can reach PG&E by calling 1-800-652-4712 (toll free) Monday through Friday, from 7 a.m. – 11 p.m., or after hours by calling the California Relay Service at 7-1-1 or 1-800-735-2929.  Visit Language Services 1-800-652-4712

Language Translations for Customers General information regarding PG&E services is available 24 hours a day. When calling, please ask for translation services.Chinese: 1-800-893-9555 Spanish: 1-800-660-6789 Vietnamese: 1-800-298-8438 English and All Other Languages: 1-800-743-5000


















