Close



1
									Current Scam(s)
								





1Guard against scams 
ALERT TYPE: Information


Customers report calls or emails from scammers posing as PG&E.
These are fraudulent attempts to collect payments from prepaid cards, represent a PG&E initiative, or sell a service such as "solar evaluation."
Beware of requests for your personal information.
Get more scam details and prevention tips


















