Get a personalized rate analysis

Sign in to your online account to view your energy use and compare rate plan options. Check plan details, including rate schedules tailored to your business needs.


Compare rate plans

























Avoid bill surprises with Energy Alerts

It's easier to stay on top of your business’s monthly bill with Energy Alerts. Just sign in to your online account and set your alert limit. You'll receive a notification by email, phone or text when your usage in on the rise.


Sign up now













Don't miss the Small Business Expo

Join us at the August 17 Expo and ask a PG&E Energy Advisor about best rates and money-saving options for your business.


Register now for free













Get 0% interest financing

Get financing up to $100,000 when you upgrade to new, energy-efficient equipment for your business through our Energy Efficiency Financing program.


Review financing options














